<br>
shock of magic ratio(avg): 3.5<br>
POP draught ratio: 3.73<br>
<br>
consider for a minute that our magic draught has a stupid stun component on it, which adds aggro, making it effectively useless except when you want to reverse kite(which is ineffective anyway mostly). this and draught of thunder are the crowning of wizard uselessness: one's a useless draught, and the other an inferior big nuke. so I think if shock of magic were given a -50 resist check, it'd become a worthy spell for being able to do fast damage and *still* have a worse ratio than even draughts.<br>
<br>
soe- make som useful! the +20 to the resist check is ridiculous. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kyron>Kyron</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 313<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/26/03 5:11 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shock of Magic should be made draught like!</span><hr size=1> how about a 0 resist adjust and a damage range of 1800 to 3000, then it would have an expected 4:1 base ratio (slightly worse then SoS) but its lower cast time would balance it out. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=istari@graffeswizardcompilation>Istari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 290<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/26/03 5:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hmm</span><hr size=1> some sort of tweaking to this spell NEEDS to be done, but its existence in the first place is rather silly. it should be a spell that fills some sort of unique purpose, as we already have agnarr's as a big nuke. then I figure it could be neat for there to be a 'big draught' despite its worsened ratio. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=whizbangdustyboots>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder Arcanist<BR>Gnomus Originalus</span><br>  Posts: 1